  "text": "As previously mentioned, an alternative approach for solving the synchronization problem was initially introduced in [CITATION_1] for the group SO(2) of planar rotations, and relied on casting the synchronization problem as a semidefinite programming (SDP) optimization problem. The objective function in (2.1) can be written as n i,j=1",
